text: Anastasija Čumika (born 7 December 1996) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club FS Metta. She has been a member of the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:FK Liepājas Metalurgs (women) players
